{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":3000,"text":"Alisa Volkman: So this is where our story begins --"},{"time":6000,"text":"the dramatic moments of the birth"},{"time":8000,"text":"of our first son, Declan."},{"time":10000,"text":"Obviously a really profound moment,"},{"time":12000,"text":"and it changed our lives in many ways."},{"time":14000,"text":"It also changed our lives in many unexpected ways,"},{"time":16000,"text":"and those unexpected ways we later reflected on,"},{"time":19000,"text":"that eventually spawned a business idea between the two of us,"},{"time":21000,"text":"and a year later, we launched Babble,"},{"time":23000,"text":"a website for parents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25000,"text":"Rufus Griscom: Now I think of our story"},{"time":27000,"text":"as starting a few years earlier. AV: That's true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"RG: You may remember, we fell head over heels in love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"AV: We did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35000,"text":"RG: We were at the time running a very different kind of website."},{"time":37000,"text":"It was a website called Nerve.com,"},{"time":39000,"text":"the tagline of which was \"literate smut.\""},{"time":42000,"text":"It was in theory, and hopefully in practice,"},{"time":45000,"text":"a smart online magazine"},{"time":47000,"text":"about sex and culture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50000,"text":"AV: That spawned a dating site."},{"time":53000,"text":"But you can understand the jokes that we get. Sex begets babies."},{"time":55000,"text":"You follow instructions on Nerve and you should end up on Babble,"},{"time":58000,"text":"which we did."},{"time":60000,"text":"And we might launch a geriatric site as our third. We'll see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64000,"text":"RG: But for us, the continuity between Nerve and Babble"},{"time":67000,"text":"was not just the life stage thing,"},{"time":69000,"text":"which is, of course, relevant,"},{"time":71000,"text":"but it was really more about"},{"time":73000,"text":"our desire to speak very honestly"},{"time":75000,"text":"about subjects that people have difficulty speaking honestly about."},{"time":78000,"text":"It seems to us that"},{"time":80000,"text":"when people start dissembling, people start lying about things,"},{"time":83000,"text":"that's when it gets really interesting."},{"time":85000,"text":"That's a subject that we want to dive into."},{"time":87000,"text":"And we've been surprised to find, as young parents,"},{"time":89000,"text":"that there are almost more taboos around parenting"},{"time":92000,"text":"than there are around sex."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94000,"text":"AV: It's true. So like we said,"},{"time":96000,"text":"the early years were really wonderful,"},{"time":98000,"text":"but they were also really difficult."},{"time":100000,"text":"And we feel like some of that difficulty"},{"time":102000,"text":"was because of this false advertisement around parenting."},{"time":105000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":107000,"text":"We subscribed to a lot of magazines, did our homework,"},{"time":110000,"text":"but really everywhere you look around, we were surrounded by images like this."},{"time":113000,"text":"And we went into parenting"},{"time":115000,"text":"expecting our lives to look like this."},{"time":117000,"text":"The sun was always streaming in, and our children would never be crying."},{"time":120000,"text":"I would always be perfectly coiffed and well rested,"},{"time":124000,"text":"and in fact, it was not like that at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"RG: When we lowered the glossy parenting magazine"},{"time":129000,"text":"that we were looking at, with these beautiful images,"},{"time":131000,"text":"and looked at the scene in our actual living room,"},{"time":133000,"text":"it looked a little bit more like this."},{"time":135000,"text":"These are our three sons."},{"time":137000,"text":"And of course, they're not always crying and screaming,"},{"time":139000,"text":"but with three boys, there's a decent probability"},{"time":141000,"text":"that at least one of them will not be comporting himself"},{"time":143000,"text":"exactly as he should."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145000,"text":"AV: Yes, you can see where the disconnect was happening for us."},{"time":148000,"text":"We really felt like what we went in expecting"},{"time":151000,"text":"had nothing to do with what we were actually experiencing,"},{"time":154000,"text":"and so we decided we really wanted to give it to parents straight."},{"time":157000,"text":"We really wanted to let them understand"},{"time":160000,"text":"what the realities of parenting were in an honest way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163000,"text":"RG: So today, what we would love to do"},{"time":165000,"text":"is share with you four parenting taboos."},{"time":168000,"text":"And of course, there are many more than four things"},{"time":170000,"text":"you can't say about parenting,"},{"time":172000,"text":"but we would like to share with you today"},{"time":174000,"text":"four that are particularly relevant for us personally."},{"time":177000,"text":"So the first, taboo number one:"},{"time":180000,"text":"you can't say you didn't fall in love with your baby"},{"time":183000,"text":"in the very first minute."},{"time":185000,"text":"I remember vividly, sitting there in the hospital."},{"time":188000,"text":"We were in the process of giving birth to our first child."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191000,"text":"AV: We, or I?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"RG: I'm sorry."},{"time":195000,"text":"Misuse of the pronoun."},{"time":197000,"text":"Alisa was very generously in the process"},{"time":199000,"text":"of giving birth to our first child -- (AV: Thank you.)"},{"time":201000,"text":"-- and I was there with a catcher's mitt."},{"time":203000,"text":"And I was there with my arms open."},{"time":205000,"text":"The nurse was coming at me"},{"time":207000,"text":"with this beautiful, beautiful child,"},{"time":209000,"text":"and I remember, as she was approaching me,"},{"time":211000,"text":"the voices of friends saying,"},{"time":214000,"text":"\"The moment they put the baby in your hands,"},{"time":216000,"text":"you will feel a sense of love that will come over you"},{"time":219000,"text":"that is [on] an order of magnitude more powerful"},{"time":221000,"text":"than anything you've ever experienced in your entire life.\""},{"time":224000,"text":"So I was bracing myself for the moment."},{"time":226000,"text":"The baby was coming,"},{"time":228000,"text":"and I was ready for this Mack truck of love"},{"time":230000,"text":"to just knock me off my feet."},{"time":233000,"text":"And instead, when the baby was placed in my hands,"},{"time":236000,"text":"it was an extraordinary moment."},{"time":238000,"text":"This picture is from literally a few seconds after"},{"time":241000,"text":"the baby was placed in my hands and I brought him over."},{"time":244000,"text":"And you can see, our eyes were glistening."},{"time":246000,"text":"I was overwhelmed with love and affection for my wife,"},{"time":249000,"text":"with deep, deep gratitude"},{"time":251000,"text":"that we had what appeared to be a healthy child."},{"time":253000,"text":"And it was also, of course, surreal."},{"time":255000,"text":"I mean, I had to check the tags and make sure."},{"time":257000,"text":"I was incredulous, \"Are you sure this is our child?\""},{"time":259000,"text":"And this was all quite remarkable."},{"time":262000,"text":"But what I felt towards the child at that moment was deep affection,"},{"time":265000,"text":"but nothing like what I feel for him now, five years later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268000,"text":"And so we've done something here"},{"time":270000,"text":"that is heretical."},{"time":272000,"text":"We have charted"},{"time":275000,"text":"our love for our child over time."},{"time":278000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":280000,"text":"This, as you know, is an act of heresy."},{"time":283000,"text":"You're not allowed to chart love."},{"time":285000,"text":"The reason you're not allowed to chart love"},{"time":287000,"text":"is because we think of love as a binary thing."},{"time":289000,"text":"You're either in love, or you're not in love."},{"time":291000,"text":"You love, or you don't love."},{"time":293000,"text":"And I think the reality is that love is a process,"},{"time":296000,"text":"and I think the problem with thinking of love"},{"time":298000,"text":"as something that's binary"},{"time":300000,"text":"is that it causes us"},{"time":302000,"text":"to be unduly concerned"},{"time":304000,"text":"that love is fraudulent, or inadequate, or what have you."},{"time":307000,"text":"And I think I'm speaking obviously here to the father's experience."},{"time":310000,"text":"But I think a lot of men do go through this sense"},{"time":312000,"text":"in the early months, maybe their first year,"},{"time":315000,"text":"that their emotional response is inadequate in some fashion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318000,"text":"AV: Well, I'm glad Rufus is bringing this up,"},{"time":320000,"text":"because you can notice where he dips in the first years"},{"time":323000,"text":"where I think I was doing most of the work."},{"time":326000,"text":"But we like to joke,"},{"time":328000,"text":"in the first few months of all of our children's lives,"},{"time":330000,"text":"this is Uncle Rufus."},{"time":332000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":334000,"text":"RG: I'm a very affectionate uncle, very affectionate uncle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336000,"text":"AV: Yes, and I often joke with Rufus when he comes home"},{"time":339000,"text":"that I'm not sure he would actually be able to find our child in a line-up"},{"time":342000,"text":"amongst other babies."},{"time":344000,"text":"So I actually threw a pop quiz here onto Rufus."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346000,"text":"RG: Uh oh."}]},{"cues":[{"time":348000,"text":"AV: I don't want to embarrass him too much. But I am going to give him three seconds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351000,"text":"RG: That is not fair. This is a trick question. He's not up there, is he?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":354000,"text":"AV: Our eight-week-old son is somewhere in here,"},{"time":357000,"text":"and I want to see if Rufus can actually quickly identify him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359000,"text":"RG: The far left. AV: No!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":361000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":368000,"text":"RG: Cruel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370000,"text":"AV: Nothing more to be said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":374000,"text":"I'll move on to taboo number two."},{"time":376000,"text":"You can't talk about how lonely having a baby can be."},{"time":379000,"text":"I enjoyed being pregnant. I loved it."},{"time":381000,"text":"I felt incredibly connected to the community around me."},{"time":384000,"text":"I felt like everyone was participating in my pregnancy, all around me,"},{"time":387000,"text":"tracking it down till the actual due-date."},{"time":391000,"text":"I felt like I was a vessel of the future of humanity."},{"time":394000,"text":"That continued into the the hospital. It was really exhilarating."},{"time":397000,"text":"I was shower with gifts and flowers and visitors."},{"time":400000,"text":"It was a really wonderful experience,"},{"time":403000,"text":"but when I got home,"},{"time":405000,"text":"I suddenly felt very disconnected"},{"time":407000,"text":"and suddenly shut in and shut out,"},{"time":410000,"text":"and I was really surprised by those feelings."},{"time":412000,"text":"I did expect it to be difficult,"},{"time":414000,"text":"have sleepless nights, constant feedings,"},{"time":416000,"text":"but I did not expect the feelings"},{"time":418000,"text":"of isolation and loneliness that I experienced,"},{"time":421000,"text":"and I was really surprised that no one had talked to me,"},{"time":423000,"text":"that I was going to be feeling this way."},{"time":425000,"text":"And I called my sister"},{"time":427000,"text":"whom I'm very close to -- and had three children --"},{"time":430000,"text":"and I asked her, \"Why didn't you tell me"},{"time":432000,"text":"I was going to be feeling this way,"},{"time":434000,"text":"that I was going to have these -- feeling incredibly isolated?\""},{"time":438000,"text":"And she said -- I'll never forget --"},{"time":440000,"text":"\"It's just not something you want to say to a mother"},{"time":442000,"text":"that's having a baby for the first time.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":445000,"text":"RG: And of course, we think"},{"time":447000,"text":"it's precisely what you really should be saying"},{"time":450000,"text":"to mothers who have kids for the first time."},{"time":453000,"text":"And that this, of course, one of the themes for us"},{"time":456000,"text":"is that we think"},{"time":458000,"text":"that candor and brutal honesty"},{"time":460000,"text":"is critical to us collectively"},{"time":462000,"text":"being great parents."},{"time":464000,"text":"And it's hard not to think"},{"time":466000,"text":"that part of what leads to this sense of isolation"},{"time":468000,"text":"is our modern world."},{"time":470000,"text":"So Alisa's experience is not isolated."},{"time":472000,"text":"So your 58 percent of mothers surveyed"},{"time":474000,"text":"report feelings of loneliness."},{"time":476000,"text":"Of those, 67 percent are most lonely"},{"time":478000,"text":"when their kids are zero to five -- probably really zero to two."},{"time":481000,"text":"In the process of preparing this,"},{"time":483000,"text":"we looked at how some other cultures around the world"},{"time":485000,"text":"deal with this period of time,"},{"time":488000,"text":"because here in the Western world,"},{"time":490000,"text":"less than 50 percent of us live near our family members,"},{"time":493000,"text":"which I think is part of why this is such a tough period."},{"time":496000,"text":"So to take one example among many:"},{"time":498000,"text":"in Southern India"},{"time":500000,"text":"there's a practice known as jholabhari,"},{"time":502000,"text":"in which the pregnant woman, when she's seven or eight months pregnant,"},{"time":505000,"text":"moves in with her mother"},{"time":507000,"text":"and goes through a series of rituals and ceremonies,"},{"time":509000,"text":"give birth and returns home to her nuclear family"},{"time":512000,"text":"several months after the child is born."},{"time":514000,"text":"And this is one of many ways"},{"time":516000,"text":"that we think other cultures offset this kind of lonely period."}]},{"cues":[{"time":519000,"text":"AV: So taboo number three:"},{"time":521000,"text":"you can't talk about your miscarriage -- but today I'll talk about mine."},{"time":524000,"text":"So after we had Declan,"},{"time":526000,"text":"we kind of recalibrated our expectations."},{"time":528000,"text":"We thought we actually could go through this again"},{"time":531000,"text":"and thought we knew what we would be up against."},{"time":534000,"text":"And we were grateful that I was able to get pregnant,"},{"time":537000,"text":"and I soon learned that we were having a boy,"},{"time":539000,"text":"and then when I was five months,"},{"time":541000,"text":"we learned that we had lost our child."},{"time":543000,"text":"This is actually the last little image we have of him."},{"time":547000,"text":"And it was obviously a very difficult time --"},{"time":549000,"text":"really painful."},{"time":552000,"text":"As I was working through that mourning process,"},{"time":555000,"text":"I was amazed that I didn't want to see anybody."},{"time":558000,"text":"I really wanted to crawl into a hole,"},{"time":561000,"text":"and I didn't really know how I was going"},{"time":563000,"text":"to work my way back into my surrounding community."},{"time":566000,"text":"And I realize, I think, the way I was feeling that way,"},{"time":569000,"text":"is on a really deep gut level,"},{"time":571000,"text":"I was feeling a lot of shame"},{"time":574000,"text":"and embarrassed, frankly,"},{"time":576000,"text":"that, in some respects, I had failed"},{"time":578000,"text":"at delivering what I'm genetically engineered to do."},{"time":581000,"text":"And of course, it made me question,"},{"time":583000,"text":"if I wasn't able to have another child,"},{"time":585000,"text":"what would that mean for my marriage,"},{"time":587000,"text":"and just me as a woman."},{"time":589000,"text":"So it was a very difficult time."},{"time":591000,"text":"As I started working through it more,"},{"time":593000,"text":"I started climbing out of that hole and talking with other people."},{"time":596000,"text":"I was really amazed"},{"time":598000,"text":"by all the stories that started flooding in."},{"time":600000,"text":"People I interacted with daily,"},{"time":602000,"text":"worked with, was friends with,"},{"time":604000,"text":"family members that I had known a long time,"},{"time":606000,"text":"had never shared with me their own stories."},{"time":608000,"text":"And I just remember feeling all these stories came out of the woodwork,"},{"time":611000,"text":"and I felt like I happened upon"},{"time":613000,"text":"this secret society of women that I now was a part of,"},{"time":616000,"text":"which was reassuring and also really concerning."},{"time":620000,"text":"And I think,"},{"time":622000,"text":"miscarriage is an invisible loss."},{"time":624000,"text":"There's not really a lot of community support around it."},{"time":626000,"text":"There's really no ceremony,"},{"time":628000,"text":"rituals, or rites."},{"time":630000,"text":"And I think, with a death, you have a funeral, you celebrate the life,"},{"time":633000,"text":"and there's a lot of community support,"},{"time":635000,"text":"and it's something women don't have with miscarriage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637000,"text":"RG: Which is too bad because, of course,"},{"time":639000,"text":"it's a very common and very traumatic experience."},{"time":641000,"text":"Fifteen to 20 percent of all pregnancies result in miscarriage,"},{"time":644000,"text":"and I find this astounding."},{"time":646000,"text":"In a survey, 74 percent of women said"},{"time":648000,"text":"that miscarriage, they felt, was partly their fault, which is awful."},{"time":651000,"text":"And astoundingly, 22 percent"},{"time":653000,"text":"said they would hide a miscarriage from their spouse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":655000,"text":"So taboo number four:"},{"time":657000,"text":"you can't say that your average happiness"},{"time":660000,"text":"has declined since having a child."},{"time":663000,"text":"The party line is that every single aspect of my life"},{"time":666000,"text":"has just gotten dramatically better"},{"time":668000,"text":"ever since I participated"},{"time":670000,"text":"in the miracle that is childbirth and family."},{"time":674000,"text":"I'll never forget, I remember vividly to this day,"},{"time":677000,"text":"our first son, Declan, was nine months old,"},{"time":680000,"text":"and I was sitting there on the couch,"},{"time":682000,"text":"and I was reading Daniel Gilbert's wonderful book, \"Stumbling on Happiness.\""},{"time":685000,"text":"And I got about two-thirds of the way through,"},{"time":687000,"text":"and there was a chart on the right-hand side --"},{"time":690000,"text":"on the right-hand page --"},{"time":692000,"text":"that we've labeled here"},{"time":694000,"text":"\"The Most Terrifying Chart Imaginable"},{"time":696000,"text":"for a New Parent.\""},{"time":698000,"text":"This chart is comprised of four completely independent studies."},{"time":701000,"text":"Basically, there's this precipitous drop"},{"time":704000,"text":"of marital satisfaction,"},{"time":706000,"text":"which is closely aligned, we all know, with broader happiness,"},{"time":709000,"text":"that doesn't rise again"},{"time":711000,"text":"until your first child goes to college."},{"time":714000,"text":"So I'm sitting here looking at the next two decades of my life,"},{"time":717000,"text":"this chasm of happiness"},{"time":719000,"text":"that we're driving our proverbial convertible straight into."},{"time":722000,"text":"We were despondent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725000,"text":"AV: So you can imagine, I mean again, the first few months were difficult,"},{"time":727000,"text":"but we'd come out of it,"},{"time":729000,"text":"and were really shocked to see this study."},{"time":731000,"text":"So we really wanted to take a deeper look at it"},{"time":734000,"text":"in hopes that we would find a silver lining."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736000,"text":"RG: And that's when it's great to be running a website for parents,"},{"time":738000,"text":"because we got this incredible reporter"},{"time":741000,"text":"to go and interview all the scientists"},{"time":744000,"text":"who conducted these four studies."},{"time":746000,"text":"We said, something is wrong here."},{"time":748000,"text":"There's something missing from these studies."},{"time":750000,"text":"It can't possibly be that bad."},{"time":754000,"text":"So Liz Mitchell did a wonderful job with this piece,"},{"time":757000,"text":"and she interviewed four scientists,"},{"time":760000,"text":"and she also interviewed Daniel Gilbert,"},{"time":762000,"text":"and we did indeed find a silver lining."},{"time":764000,"text":"So this is our guess"},{"time":766000,"text":"as to what this baseline of average happiness"},{"time":769000,"text":"arguably looks like throughout life."},{"time":771000,"text":"Average happiness is, of course, inadequate,"},{"time":773000,"text":"because it doesn't speak"},{"time":775000,"text":"to the moment-by-moment experience,"},{"time":777000,"text":"and so this is what we think it looks like"},{"time":780000,"text":"when you layer in"},{"time":782000,"text":"moment-to-moment experience."},{"time":785000,"text":"And so we all remember as children,"},{"time":787000,"text":"the tiniest little thing -- and we see it on the faces of our children --"},{"time":790000,"text":"the teeniest little thing"},{"time":792000,"text":"can just rocket them to these heights"},{"time":794000,"text":"of just utter adulation,"},{"time":796000,"text":"and then the next teeniest little thing"},{"time":798000,"text":"can cause them just to plummet to the depths of despair."},{"time":800000,"text":"And it's just extraordinary to watch, and we remember it ourselves."},{"time":803000,"text":"And then, of course, as you get older,"},{"time":805000,"text":"it's almost like age is a form of lithium."}]},{"cues":[{"time":807000,"text":"As you get older, you become more stable."},{"time":810000,"text":"And part of what happens, I think, in your '20s and '30s,"},{"time":813000,"text":"is you start to learn to hedge your happiness."},{"time":815000,"text":"You start to realize that"},{"time":817000,"text":"\"Hey, I could go to this live music event"},{"time":820000,"text":"and have an utterly transforming experience"},{"time":822000,"text":"that will cover my entire body with goosebumps,"},{"time":825000,"text":"but it's more likely that I'll feel claustrophobic"},{"time":827000,"text":"and I won't be able to get a beer."},{"time":830000,"text":"So I'm not going to go."},{"time":832000,"text":"I've got a good stereo at home. So, I'm not going to go.\""},{"time":835000,"text":"So your average happiness goes up,"},{"time":838000,"text":"but you lose those transcendent moments."}]},{"cues":[{"time":840000,"text":"AV: Yeah, and then you have your first child,"},{"time":843000,"text":"and then you really resubmit yourself"},{"time":845000,"text":"to these highs and lows --"},{"time":847000,"text":"the highs being the first steps, the first smile,"},{"time":850000,"text":"your child reading to you for the first time --"},{"time":852000,"text":"the lows being, our house, any time from six to seven every night."},{"time":857000,"text":"But you realize you resubmit yourself"},{"time":859000,"text":"to losing control in a really wonderful way,"},{"time":862000,"text":"which we think provides a lot of meaning to our lives"},{"time":864000,"text":"and is quite gratifying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":866000,"text":"RG: And so in effect,"},{"time":868000,"text":"we trade average happiness."},{"time":870000,"text":"We trade the sort of security and safety"},{"time":872000,"text":"of a certain level of contentment"},{"time":874000,"text":"for these transcendent moments."},{"time":877000,"text":"So where does that leave the two of us"},{"time":879000,"text":"as a family with our three little boys"},{"time":881000,"text":"in the thick of all this?"},{"time":883000,"text":"There's another factor in our case."},{"time":885000,"text":"We have violated yet another taboo"},{"time":887000,"text":"in our own lives,"},{"time":889000,"text":"and this is a bonus taboo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":892000,"text":"AV: A quick bonus taboo for you, that we should not be working together,"},{"time":895000,"text":"especially with three children --"},{"time":897000,"text":"and we are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":899000,"text":"RG: And we had reservations about this on the front end."},{"time":902000,"text":"Everybody knows, you should absolutely not work with your spouse."},{"time":905000,"text":"In fact, when we first went out to raise money to start Babble,"},{"time":908000,"text":"the venture capitalists said,"},{"time":910000,"text":"\"We categorically don't invest"},{"time":912000,"text":"in companies founded by husbands and wives,"},{"time":914000,"text":"because there's an extra point of failure."},{"time":916000,"text":"It's a bad idea. Don't do it.\""},{"time":918000,"text":"And we obviously went forward. We did."},{"time":920000,"text":"We raised the money, and we're thrilled that we did,"},{"time":923000,"text":"because in this phase of one's life,"},{"time":925000,"text":"the incredibly scarce resource is time."},{"time":928000,"text":"And if you're really passionate about what you do every day -- which we are --"},{"time":931000,"text":"and you're also passionate about your relationship,"},{"time":933000,"text":"this is the only way we know how to do it."},{"time":936000,"text":"And so the final question that we would ask is:"},{"time":938000,"text":"can we collectively bend that happiness chart upwards?"},{"time":941000,"text":"It's great that we have these transcendent moments of joy,"},{"time":944000,"text":"but they're sometimes pretty quick."},{"time":947000,"text":"And so how about that average baseline of happiness?"},{"time":950000,"text":"Can we move that up a little bit?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":952000,"text":"AV: And we kind of feel that the happiness gap, which we talked about,"},{"time":955000,"text":"is really the result of walking into parenting --"},{"time":957000,"text":"and really any long-term partnership for that matter --"},{"time":959000,"text":"with the wrong expectations."},{"time":961000,"text":"And if you have the right expectations and expectation management,"},{"time":964000,"text":"we feel like it's going to be a pretty gratifying experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":967000,"text":"RG: And so this is what --"},{"time":969000,"text":"And we think that a lot of parents,"},{"time":971000,"text":"when you get in there -- in our case anyway --"},{"time":973000,"text":"you pack your bags for a trip to Europe, and you're really excited to go."},{"time":976000,"text":"Get out of the airplane,"},{"time":978000,"text":"it turns out you're trekking in Nepal."},{"time":980000,"text":"And trekking in Nepal is an extraordinary experience,"},{"time":983000,"text":"particularly if you pack your bags properly"},{"time":985000,"text":"and you know what you're getting in for and you're psyched."},{"time":987000,"text":"So the point of all this for us today"},{"time":989000,"text":"is not just hopefully honesty for the sake of honesty,"},{"time":992000,"text":"but a hope that by being more honest and candid about these experiences,"},{"time":995000,"text":"that we can all collectively"},{"time":997000,"text":"bend that happiness baseline up a little bit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1000000,"text":"RG + AV: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1002000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}